---
---

<section class="section" id="features" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="section-label">// What you get</div>
  <h2>EVERYTHING YOUR<br />SOCIAL TEAM WISHES<br />THEY HAD TIME FOR.</h2>
  <div class="features-grid fade-in">
    <div class="feature-cell dark">
      <span class="feature-icon">&#x1f3ad;</span>
      <h3>Trending Meme Templates</h3>
      <p>Always-fresh meme formats pulled from what's actually working right now — not templates from 2019.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-cell">
      <span class="feature-icon">&#x1f3ac;</span>
      <h3>Video Memes Included</h3>
      <p>Growth and Agency plans include AI-generated video memes. Perfect for TikTok, Instagram Reels, and YouTube Shorts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-cell accent">
      <span class="feature-icon">&#9997;&#65039;</span>
      <h3>Platform Captions Written For You</h3>
      <p>Every meme ships with 3 captions — one for LinkedIn, one for Instagram, one for TikTok. Copy. Paste. Post.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-cell">
      <span class="feature-icon">&#x1f4f0;</span>
      <h3>Weekly Auto-Newsletter</h3>
      <p>A fully written newsletter with your meme pack, top review highlights, and a CTA. Sent to your inbox every Monday morning.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-cell">
      <span class="feature-icon">&#x1f504;</span>
      <h3>One-Click Regenerate</h3>
      <p>Don't love a meme? Regenerate it instantly. Edit the text. Swap the template. You're always in control.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-cell dark">
      <span class="feature-icon">&#x1f4e6;</span>
      <h3>Download Packs or Push to Notion</h3>
      <p>Download a ZIP, push to a Notion content calendar, or connect Buffer to schedule posts automatically.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      margin-top: 64px;
    }
  }

  .feature-cell {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .feature-cell {
      padding: 48px 40px;
    }
  }

  .feature-cell:hover {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .feature-cell.dark {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .feature-cell.dark:hover {
    background: #111;
  }

  .feature-cell.accent {
    background: var(--orange);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .feature-cell.accent:hover {
    background: var(--orange-hover);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  }

  .feature-cell h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 26px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .feature-cell h3 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }
  }

  .feature-cell p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .feature-cell p {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }

  .feature-cell.dark h3 {
    color: var(--cream);
  }

  .feature-cell.dark p {
    color: #aaa;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .feature-cell.accent h3 {
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .feature-cell.accent p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
